1
00:00:47,160 --> 00:00:48,280
Syrus, the Western Merchant

2
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:49,160
Who recognizes him?

3
00:00:53,440 --> 00:00:53,760
My Lord

4
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:54,800
I do

5
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:57,360
This man has a brandy nose

6
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:58,560
He has a great capacity for liquor

7
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:01,000
I once drank with him all night

8
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:03,640
When was the last time you saw him?

9
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:05,160
Probably

10
00:01:05,520 --> 00:01:06,600
Seven or eight days ago

11
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:07,960
I was returning from the Western Regions

12
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,640
and rested at the Ten Thousand Nations Inn

13
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:12,440
When I sobered up the next day, he was gone

14
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:14,520
He must have gone to Chang'an early in the morning

15
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:22,440
That was exactly seven days ago

16
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:26,360
Adudan the Arab. Who recognizes him?

17
00:01:27,160 --> 00:01:27,400
I do

18
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:28,680
Me

19
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:47,880
Lao Yao

20
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:48,720
Mm

21
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:50,320
This forest is sinister

22
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,240
I fear it is far beyond our imagination

23
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:53,360
I realized that

24
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,280
According to the map

25
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,080
we should have reached Wanling Township long ago

26
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,560
but now we can't seem to find our way out of this forest

27
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:26,800
Lao Yao

28
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,160
Lao Yao

29
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:31,720
Lao Yao

30
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:33,960
Lao Yao

31
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:38,800
Lao Yao

32
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,720
Lao Yao, can you hear me?

33
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:44,080
Shentu

34
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,000
Here

35
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:47,600
The road is this way

36
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:57,800
Shentu

37
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:07,640
What's wrong, Shentu?

38
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,040
Cover your mouth and nose

39
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:11,680
There is a Bewildering Fog in the forest

40
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,640
It seems we are already trapped in the forest

41
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:47,240
It's her

42
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:49,480
That wrongful case

43
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,760
Shentu Boqi

44
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,960
As a Magistrate

45
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,040
yet you misjudged a wrongful case

46
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:14,720
You deserve to die!

47
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,000
You deserve to die!

48
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,840
You deserve to die

49
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:23,880
You deserve to die

50
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,280
You wronged an innocent person

51
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:26,800
Go die right now

52
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,640
Go die right now

53
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,080
Die!

54
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:33,240
Die!

55
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:35,800
Shentu Boqi

56
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,160
You are unworthy of being a Magistrate

57
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,800
Die!

58
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,080
Shentu

59
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:39,960
Die!

60
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:40,680
Shentu, wake up

61
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,320
Die

62
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:41,680
Shentu

63
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:42,880
Die

64
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:43,640
Die

65
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,400
Die

66
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:45,640
Die

67
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:02,680
No

68
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,240
I cannot fall here

69
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,200
Bad news!

70
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:34,440
Something terrible has happened!

71
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,400
Village Head! Village Head! Someone else has died!

72
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:37,560
What?

73
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,720
Shentu, you're awake.

74
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,400
Where is this?

75
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,640
If I hadn't stopped you last night...

76
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,520
...you would have stabbed yourself to death.

77
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:01,840
This is Brother Sun Jia.

78
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:04,200
He's the one who saved us last night.

79
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:05,240
Oh, thank you.

80
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,320
You are too kind, sir.

81
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:07,880
I wouldn't call it saving.

82
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:09,720
I was just returning from buying lamp oil...

83
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,400
...when I happened upon you two lost in the forest.

84
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,240
Lao Yao.

85
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:13,880
Yeah?

86
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,680
Wanling Township is haunted.

87
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,200
I feel the truth...

88
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:19,600
...lies right in this forest.

89
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,280
You two...

90
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:24,800
...came here for the spirits?

91
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:25,720
Exactly.

92
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,000
You are outsiders.

93
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:28,920
You may not know...

94
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:31,320
...but you must not go into that forest again.

95
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:33,120
Since you are awake...

96
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,000
...and it's safer while it's light out...

97
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,640
...let me lead you out.

98
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:39,000
Wanling Township is no place to stay.

99
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,560
That forest...

100
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:42,800
...what is strange about it?

101
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,440
It is the Vengeful spirit of the mountains.

102
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:48,480
Nonsense.

103
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,960
There are no such things as ghosts or spirits in this world.

104
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:53,360
It is easy to enter Wanling Township...

105
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,000
...but to leave...

106
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,080
...the only way is through the old forest.

107
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,360
Nowadays, only...

108
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:00,160
...those who regularly buy lamp oil dare to walk it.

109
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:02,080
If no one guides you...

110
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:05,160
...you will never leave Wanling Township.

111
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,480
Good advice cannot save a damned soul.

112
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,960
Since you two do not believe me...

113
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:12,480
...suit yourselves.

114
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,120
Another death!

115
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:15,800
Someone else has died!

116
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:16,880
Let's go take a look.

117
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,040
Let's go.

118
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:31,720
Village Head.

119
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,320
This Red bridal dress...

120
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,120
I'm not blind.

121
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:38,800
Where is her father?

122
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:40,400
We are looking for him now.

123
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:41,280
We haven't found him yet.

124
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:43,960
What are you standing there for?

125
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,040
Go find him immediately!

126
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,720
Get more people to help!

127
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,240
Yes!

128
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:48,400
Go!

129
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:58,640
The oil lamp... it's out.

130
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:12,560
Bury her.

131
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,320
While it is still light...

132
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:16,600
...bury her in the forest quickly.

133
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,040
Bury her far away.

134
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,760
Do not invite the ghost into the village...

135
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,680
...to harm the people.

136
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:25,680
Wait.

137
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,680
Since a murder has occurred...

138
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:37,720
...why bury the body hastily without investigating the cause?

139
00:08:38,800 --> 00:08:40,200
Who are you two?

140
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:43,360
Acting Vice Minister of the Dali Temple...

141
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,360
...Yao Yuan.

142
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:48,920
You guys go that way.

143
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:50,520
Go.

144
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:53,280
Check up there.

145
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,160
You guys search over there.

146
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,280
You guys search over there.

147
00:08:58,040 --> 00:08:58,200
Go.

148
00:08:58,560 --> 00:08:59,040
Brother Jia Liang...

149
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,000
...we can't stay in Wanling Township anymore.

150
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:02,360
Why don't we leave?

151
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,600
Burning oil every day...

152
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:06,040
...we'll burn through our money and die anyway.

153
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:06,760
Leave?

154
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:09,200
Why did we come to Wanling Township in the first place?

155
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,680
Where can we go now?

156
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:11,840
Hurry up!

157
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:12,640
Go find him!

158
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:16,920
Found him!

159
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:18,320
Old Man Yu's body is here!

160
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:19,800
Go, go, go!
